                "html": "<p>We are excited to announce that all paying Copilot customers can now use the technical preview of GitHub Copilot Workspace.</p><p>Copilot Workspace is a Copilot-native development environment designed to help you with everyday tasks, from idea to merge.</p><p>Starting from a GitHub Issue or natural language task, you can work with Copilot Workspace to iterate on solving your problem. Together, you can:</p>",
