                "excerpt": "The latest updates to GitHub Copilot in Visual Studio Code bring powerful improvements to agent mode, code generation, and repository search to help you work faster and more seamlessly. Learn…",
                "html": "<p>The latest updates to GitHub Copilot in Visual Studio Code bring powerful improvements to agent mode, code generation, and repository search to help you work faster and more seamlessly. Learn more in the VS Code April 2025 release notes, including how to adjust these settings.</p>",
                "hasContent": true
