                "excerpt": "Supercharge your Copilot Chat: Use @ to attach references! 📎✨ Talking with GitHub Copilot Chat just got a major boost: you can now attach references for richer, more productive conversations!…",
                "html": "<p>Talking with GitHub Copilot Chat just got a major boost: you can now attach references for richer, more productive conversations!</p><p>Unlock the full power of Copilot Chat to work on your code, repositories, and issues, all right from the conversation window!</p><p>💬 We’d love your feedback! Join the GitHub Community discussion at any time.</p>",
