            "preview": {
                "excerpt": "The September 2025 update to Visual Studio brings game-changing Profiler and .NET Modernization agents, more powerful MCP interactions, and smarter code reviews. Highlights Here’s what’s new with GitHub Copilot in…",
                "html": "<p>The September 2025 update to Visual Studio brings game-changing Profiler and .NET Modernization agents, more powerful MCP interactions, and smarter code reviews.</p><p>Here’s what’s new with GitHub Copilot in Visual Studio 2022 (v17.14):</p><p>.NET Modernization Agent: Upgrade your .NET projects to the latest versions and migrate them to Azure with the help of the .NET Modernization Agent. Right-click your project and select Modernize or prompt @Modernize directly in Copilot Chat to get started.</p>",
                "hasContent": true
            }
