                "excerpt": "We’ve enhanced the GPT-4.1 Copilot code completion model in GitHub Copilot to improve the model’s ability to infer your intent from code context. As a result, you’ll see more accurate…",
                "html": "<p>We’ve enhanced the GPT-4.1 Copilot code completion model in GitHub Copilot to improve the model’s ability to infer your intent from code context. As a result, you’ll see more accurate and contextually relevant inline code suggestions. This update is available for all users on all plans.</p>",
