                "html": "<p>You can now assign issues in Linear to Copilot coding agent, our asynchronous, autonomous background agent.</p><p>When you assign a Linear issue to Copilot, it will:</p><p>We welcome your feedback. Feel free to share your thoughts in the community discussion.</p>",
