                "html": "<p>You can now access your organization’s Copilot usage metrics via the Copilot usage APIs.</p><p>The APIs contain reports with aggregated and user-specific metrics, including usage statistics for various Copilot features, user engagement data, and feature adoption metrics.</p><p>To see these metrics, the Copilot usage metrics policy must be enabled.</p>",
                "hasContent": true
