                "excerpt": "On February 13, 2026 we announced changes to the required network configuration for Copilot coding agent, taking effect on February 27. These changes only affect teams running Copilot coding agent…",
                "html": "<p>On February 13, 2026 we announced changes to the required network configuration for Copilot coding agent, taking effect on February 27.</p><p>These changes only affect teams running Copilot coding agent on self-hosted runners or larger runners with Azure private networking.</p><p>These changes have now taken effect. Copilot will apply subscription-based network routing, connecting to a different host depending on the Copilot plan of the user who initiated the agent task:</p>",
